The paper proposes a framework for ranking and filtering news-quality photos, which involves leveraging aesthetic, social, and deep-learning semantic features. This suggests that the paper could fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. However, given the focus on image ranking and filtering, cs.MM and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
